  Locus:
    Page: 418
    Verse: 10
Tags:
  - Self
---
Self-realization is nothing but seeing God literally. Our greatest mistake
is that we think of God as acting symbolically and allegorically, instead
of practically and literally. ...You must get rid of the idea that you are
yet to realize the Self. You are the Self here and now.
